{"word":"G1876 - ἐπάναγκες - epánankes - ep-an'-ang-kes - Necessary","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπάναγκες</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epánankes</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-an'-ang-kes</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Necessary</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective Neuter / பெயரடை (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"அவசியமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"necessarily"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a presumed compound of <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G318 - ἀνάγκη - anánkē - an-ang-kay'/318\">G318</a>; (adverb) <i>on necessity</i>, that is, <i>necessarily:</i> - necessary.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}